Package: AutoML4R
Type: Package
Title: Automated Machine Learning Feature Selection Workflow
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Xinyu", "Li", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "lixinyu1033472712@gmail.com")
  )
Author: Xinyu Li
Maintainer: Xinyu Li <lixinyu1033472712@gmail.com>
Description: Provides an automated machine learning workflow for feature
    selection and consensus visualization across multiple algorithms. The main
    entry point is auto_ml_analysis(), which accepts a feature matrix and group
    labels, writes model outputs, and saves feature-selection results. The
    automl4r_beautiful_plots() function generates publication-oriented
    per-algorithm selected-gene plots, diagnostic figures, expression plots,
    and Nature-style consensus voting figures.
